{
  "stem": "6526.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My house was still there, and there lived-- Poles lived there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was there almost for two weeks, sleeping and eating.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People I knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were neighbors of ours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they were very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A matter of fact, one was a friend of my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came over, he wanted to come to the States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Signed for him that he'll be responsible for him for the time being.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came here and remained here as an immigrant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We sold him the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We sold him the house that we had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after a few weeks, we went away to, to Warsaw and to Lodz, too, because there-- a few weeks before my brother came--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few weeks before my brother came, there was an incident that a man that lived in Kaluszyn, he was a kind of communist, left-- socialist, left winger-- and he wanted to become Mr.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Big Shot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because of that, they got away with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the few Jews that had the factory of the-- of the sheepskin, they were hidden by, by farmers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to leave because they were afraid they were going to kill them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you left--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when my brother and I came back, the Poles, the [NON-ENGLISH], the, the, the, the army, they call it the false army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came to us and says, you don't have to be afraid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We will do nothing to you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are-- like, we were saints to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't do anything but we didn't want to stay there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Warsaw and to Lodz and from there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
